{
  "stem": "20035.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that was the second type-- the second type of change in-- especially in French Canada, where the basic idea was that I didn't believe in and today I don't believe that because of the separatist ideas and basically disliking anybody but French-Canadians, that with the Gottlieb name my children have any-- my children will have any future, although my French even today is better than my English.",
      "word_count": 68
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My children are bilingual.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I figure that their life definitely should be anywhere where there's freedom and freedom exists.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if there's anywhere freedom exists, it's the United States of America.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And selfishly, I said that once I go to America, I prefer where the sun is shining, so we came to Florida.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "More than met.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm very, very happy, very-- I became a very proud American, who probably more American than born Americans.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For a long, long time, I didn't.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A long time I didn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was even reluctant and very, very seldom and very like in a nutshell, I was talking to my own kids.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one day, if you have enough time I tell you that I was called to my older son's school by the principal to tell me that I should be there next morning at 10 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My question well, what did he do?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What did he do wrong?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He didn't tell me, just be there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I went there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And suddenly I was ushered into the gym, where I had 300 kids sitting.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And suddenly my son gets up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had no idea where I'm going, what I'm doing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my son introduced me as an endangered specie.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my dad is going to talk about the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
